title: Unlocking the Full Potential: The Harmonious Dance of EF Core and SQL Server
abstract:
.NET 8 has improved the data story with new features, waiting to be discovered. 🕵️

Let's embark on a journey from understanding basic scaffolding to the intricacies of schema evolution and SQL debugging. It's time to be inspired by the art of database craftsmanship. 🧑‍🎨
eventShortDescription:
​.NET 8 has improved the data story with new features, waiting to be discovered. 🕵️

Let's embark on a journey from understanding basic scaffolding to the intricacies of schema evolution and SQL debugging. It's time to be inspired by the art of database craftsmanship. 🧑‍🎨

--

Join us in person from 5pm AEST in Brisbane, or 6pm AEDT in Sydney and Melbourne:

SSW Sydney – Watch party 🎦
SSW Melbourne – Watch party 🎦
SSW Brisbane – Live 🔴
